title: Jimmy Fallon honored by Harvard Lampoon
text:
> Entertainment Jimmy Fallon honored by Harvard Lampoon FILE - In this Aug. 25, 2014, file photo, Jimmy Fallon presents an award at the 66th Annual Primetime Emmy Awards in Los Angeles. Fallon got the royal treatment at Harvard. "The Tonight Show" host and "Saturday Night Live" alum was honored Saturday, Oct. 24, 2015, by the Harvard Lampoon, the country's oldest continuously published humor magazine. (Photo by Chris Pizzello/Invision/AP, File)
